INSERT {
  GRAPH narr:Tx_20260430T120000Z {
    narr:Actor_PractitionerBetaUserBarber skos:note "an early prospect's business partner at a collaborator. Expertise in pelvic floor care. Co-authoring a forthcoming book (May 21, 2026) explaining their methodology to other practitioners and patients. Has substantial podcast content but notes that many podcasts don't contain direct statements about his own practice — he talks about framing how to evaluate a good practitioner in the pelvic floor space, and it's implied he's doing those things but not directly stated. Marketing website is a constant source of frustration. Canonical Knowledge Packager archetype example alongside an early prospect. Session on April 30, 2026 (acupuncture table conversation with Scarlet) generated the practitioner marketplace design: patient-as-goal-holder payer model, trust transfer mechanic, proposal artifact, practitioner three roles, referrer gift economy. Warm beachhead for the cash-pay alternative care NYC wedge alongside an early prospect." .
  }
}
WHERE {
  GRAPH ?g {
    narr:Actor_PractitionerBetaUserBarber skos:note ?oldNote .
  }
} 